title: DJ Jonny Moiree - Erotic Mode
description:
A darkly erotic, intimately sensual, luscious journey of sound, of passion, of lust, set to Depeche Mode&#039;s finest love songs.

What can you do in 82 minutes?

Well, that&#039;s up to you and whomever you&#039;re sharing this musical experience with.  The mix will take you the edge of love and lust, over the arc of passion and tension, over to release and romance.

82-minute continuous mix, compiled by DJ Jonny Moiree.

   2. little 15 [ulrich schnauss remix] [depeche mode]
